title: Great experience !!
text:
Hi, this is Bruce

I really had a good ride home this evening. Well, it was earlier.

Thank you everybody so much I’m not a usual customer, but something happened and I really appreciate your services. ( sometimes apps can be difficult for myself.)

And also, is there any opportunity for if I book 20 days a month or any kind of service monthly or yearly?

We all know that apps and phones, and such and such can be difficult for some people.

Again, thank you so much. Can you let me know when the survey manager reads this?

Thx..

title: Pick up and drop off
text: Ok I been riding with Uber for a few years I’m in Long Beach and my address is off the beaten path sort of speak. Picking me up is correct and Uber drivers have no problem . But coming back my address is off by 2 miles at my destination and the app won’t correct my drop off address so I try to change and the same thing picks happing . I’m lucky the drivers are all cool about it and drop me at the right place and not 2 miles away but I still need Uber app to correct this issue
